gobblin.runtime.cli

Class PublicMethodsGobblinCliFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.cli.PublicMethodsGobblinCliFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EmbeddedGobblinCliFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstructorAndPublicMethodsGobblinCliFactory, EmbeddedGobblinDistcp.CliFactory

    public abstract class PublicMethodsGobblinCliFactory
extends Object
implements EmbeddedGobblinCliFactory
    A helper class for automatically inferring Options from the public methods in a class. For each public method in the class to infer with exactly zero or one String parameter, the helper will create an optional Option. Using the annotation EmbeddedGobblinCliOption the helper can automatically add a description to the Option. Annotating a method with NotOnCli will prevent the helper from creating an Option from it. For an example usage see EmbeddedGobblin.CliFactory
